            <title>[CASSANDRA-7170] socket should enable keepalive in MessagingService.SocketThread</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7170</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The number of socket fds increase over time in some nodes of one of our cassandra clusters .&lt;br/&gt;
Finally we find that the socket should enable keepalive in MessagingService.SocketThread .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the 2.x versions have fix this.&lt;br/&gt;
but the 1.x versions still have this problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
